  "texts": [
    "For the type 2 diabetes dataset, the performance is nearly perfect with scores above 0.9.",
    "In contrast, the scores for the glaucoma dataset are still good but much worse with scores around 0.7.",
    "The different possible slot fillers are shown in Table 9 in the Appendix 4.",
    "Looking at the different slot fillers, it is not immediately clear why the diabetes case is so much easier for both approaches than the glaucoma case.",
    "Both tables have approximately the same number of different entries and in both cases the journal names are in many cases trivial to recognize (containing either Diabetes or Ophthalmol).However, the distribution of occurrences might partially explain the performance differences here."
